Name: Zombie Squad
About the game: Zombie Squad, a casual game, combines tower defense and rogue like. The operation of the game is very simple, and the characters can fight automatically, just click to release their skills. In addition, the game also integrates card drawing and character training, which can be pushed through levels to obtain training resources.
